---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Results That Matter" description="Review David Glass's proven track record of infrastructure improvements, fiscal responsibility, and managed growth in Bastrop County.">
  
  <!-- Page Header -->
  <section class="page-header-gradient pt-28 pb-20 relative">
    <div class="relative z-10 max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
      <div class="gold-line mx-auto mb-6"></div>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-serif font-extrabold text-white mb-6">Results That Matter</h1>
      <p class="text-xl font-sans font-light text-white/70 leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        What we have accomplished together in Precinct 4 and across Bastrop County. We do not just make plans — we deliver outcomes.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 sm:py-24 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      
      <!-- Roads and Infrastructure -->
      <div class="mb-24 reveal">
        <div class="mb-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-navy">Roads & Infrastructure</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-near-black/70 max-w-3xl font-sans">
            Decades of deferred maintenance and unprecedented county growth demand decisive action. Here is how we are keeping Bastrop County moving.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 reveal-stagger">
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 border border-warm-gray hover-lift">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy mb-3">Targeted Mill & Overlay</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black/70 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">Dozens of miles of county roads completely rebuilt or resurfaced using sustainable techniques that stretch every tax dollar further.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 border border-warm-gray hover-lift">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy mb-3">Critical Bridge Replacements</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black/70 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">Secured funding to repair or replace aging bridges, prioritizing school bus routes and emergency response paths.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 border border-warm-gray hover-lift">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy mb-3">Comprehensive Drainage</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black/70 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">Invested heavily in clearing and rebuilding drainage channels to prevent road washout and protect private property.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Budget and Fiscal -->
      <div class="mb-24 reveal">
        <div class="mb-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 7h6m0 10v-3m-3 3h.01M9 17h.01M9 14h.01M12 14h.01M15 11h.01M12 11h.01M9 11h.01M7 21h10a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v14a2 2 0 002 2z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-navy">Budget & Fiscal Accountability</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-near-black/70 max-w-3xl font-sans">
            Every dollar the county spends comes directly from the people who live here. We manage it accordingly.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 reveal-stagger">
          <div class="page-header-gradient text-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift">
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-gold mb-3">No-Nonsense Budgeting</h3>
              <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-sans">Applying business principles to root out waste, demand efficiency, and deliver services without defaulting to tax hikes.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="page-header-gradient text-white rounded-2xl p-8 hover-lift">
            <div class="relative z-10">
              <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif font-bold text-gold mb-3">Responsible Fleet Management</h3>
              <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed font-sans">Re-evaluating county equipment lifecycle and purchasing to save taxpayers hundreds of thousands over the long term.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Growth Management -->
      <div class="mb-24 reveal">
        <div class="mb-10">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-navy/10 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-navy" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3.055 11H5a2 2 0 012 2v1a2 2 0 002 2 2 2 0 012 2v2.945M8 3.935V5.5A2.5 2.5 0 0010.5 8h.5a2 2 0 012 2 2 2 0 104 0 2 2 0 012-2h1.064M15 20.488V18a2 2 0 012-2h3.064M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-navy">Growth Management</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-near-black/70 max-w-3xl font-sans">
            Bastrop County is a prime target for developers. We ensure development serves the community, not the other way around.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 reveal-stagger">
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 border border-warm-gray hover-lift">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy mb-3">Demanding High Standards</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black/70 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">Holding developers accountable — they pay for the infrastructure required by their developments, not existing taxpayers.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 border border-warm-gray hover-lift">
             <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy mb-3">Water Security</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black/70 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">Ensuring new subdivisions have secured sustainable water rights before any ground is broken.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 border border-warm-gray hover-lift">
             <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy mb-3">Protecting Property Rights</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black/70 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">Balancing subdivision density with the fundamental rights of long-time Bastrop County landowners.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Community Investment -->
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="mb-10">
           <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-4">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-gold/15 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center">
              <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-gold" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
                <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z" />
              </svg>
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl font-serif font-bold text-navy">Community Investment</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg text-near-black/70 max-w-3xl font-sans">
            Supporting the partnerships that make Bastrop County a great place to live and work.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 reveal-stagger">
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 border-l-4 border-navy hover-lift">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy mb-3">Economic Development</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black/70 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">Working with the Elgin EDC and surrounding municipalities to attract responsible, high-paying jobs to the county.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream rounded-2xl p-6 border-l-4 border-navy hover-lift">
             <h3 class="text-xl font-serif font-bold text-navy mb-3">Emergency Preparedness</h3>
            <p class="text-near-black/70 font-sans text-sm leading-relaxed">Securing resources for volunteer fire departments and EMS to drastically improve response times in rural Precinct 4.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
